name: I'm on a watcher duty 5: Returning to Gensokyo
name_original: I'm on a watcher duty 5: Returning to Gensokyo
description:
The 5th game of my IOOD fangame series.

Story: You got requested by Yukari to go back to Gensokyo one more time because anomalies still happening there. You accepted the request and head back there immediately. You now back to your duty again.
